window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>The exciting first Chronological Man Adventure!</b></p> <p>It's 1890 and the citizens of Boston are beginning to go missing in the fog.</p> <p>The police are confounded. The public is frightened. The city is on the edge of hysteria.</p> <p>It's up to the mysterious Smith, inventor and adventurer, to figure out what's going on with the help of his assistant, April Malone. They'll have to face off against a secret society, corrupt policemen, and a mad psychologist hell-bent on dissecting Smith, in order to solve the mystery of what's going on and to save the city from an even more sinister threat.</p> <p>It's the first story of Smith, a hard science fiction time traveler with more than enough quirk to last him several centuries.</p>"; 
